reviews.text: Good food for a decent price. Menu has English but the paper you mark your order on does not. The "dry noodles with chicken nuggets" is very good! So is the passion fruit green tea with coconut jelly. Servers are kind and helpful to non-locals. (Dry noodles = not soup. Does come with a little bit of sauce at the bottom as well as ground pork on top. No bones in the chicken.)
肉燥乾面正味道唔錯，價錢合理
轉了手新店試了它的下午茶 ，份量偏少，不過32元算是差不多。可是味道一般，沒有太大驚喜。環境只是跟之前稍為改動一點，所以坐得還算舒適的。
環境舒服，裝修富文青感，食物美味，店員有禮，價錢親民，值得推介的一間台式食店！！！
